    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines extensions to the Web Distributed Authoring and Versioning (WebDAV) protocol to specify a standard way of accessing, managing, and sharing calendaring and scheduling information based on the iCalendar format.  This document defines the "calendar-access" feature of CalDAV. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
